Input composition

CDS is 91.6% for French and 79.6% for Sesotho.

In terms of CDS input composition:

  • For French It is on average 79.1% from the mother; 9.2% from adults and 3.3% from other children.

  • For Sesotho: It is on average 25.3% from the mother; 15.8% from adults and 38.5% from other children.
